com.ibm.ccl.soa.deploy.core.datamodels
Class CommunicationConstraintDataModel

java.lang.Object
  com.ibm.ccl.soa.deploy.core.datamodels.CommunicationConstraintDataModel

public class CommunicationConstraintDataModel
extends java.lang.Object

Constraint datamodel is an object container of values needed to create capablities and requirements on a given source and target unit

The following properties are required. If not provided, then the model is not in a valid state, and the operation will not be able to execute successfully.

  • targetUnit: Target for the newly created communication capability
  • sourceUnit: Source unit for newly created communication requirement
  • protocalType: Communication type, ie http, rmi...
  • port: port number is applicable
  • linkDescriptor: The LinkDescriptor property.
